  "time_ut": 1656910351,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca\u0dc4\u0dda\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca 3 \u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3 killed in a shooting in Copenhagen",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three people were killed when a man with a rifle broke into a supermarket building in Copenhagen, Denmark. The number of injured is said to be 10.",
        "The shooter was a 22-year-old tough guy. The police managed to catch the young man alive.",
        "Investigations are still going on regarding the incident, but Inspector General of Police Soren Thomason told the media that it was a terrorist attack.",
        "Some media had reported that the young man who did the shooting was Danish, and that he was a white extremist.",
        "The shooting took place at around 5.30pm Danish time in the 'Field' shopping complex building located between Copenhagen Airport and the City Center mall. It is also said that the three victims of the attack are men."
      ],
